301
00:24:55,360 --> 00:25:01,040
When you're a small startup, I don't think you 
need a lot of this overhead. It's really much  

302
00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:06,360
designed for larger scale companies, and those 
are the ones that you see really adopting it.

303
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:09,240
From what I've seen on the data, it's 
also companies that are as you I think  

