00:26:36,988 --> 00:26:37,160
Okay, cool. Let's go there. Yeah.

324
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:42,920
Scaled Agile Framework came out of the desire to 
figure out how do we scale Scrum and different  

325
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:50,600
processes and bring it to organizations at scale. 
It originated from a more structured approach to  

