00:51:51,240 --> 00:51:55,200
This process is going to fix all our problems." 
Can you talk about just the importance of that,  

611
00:51:55,200 --> 00:52:00,120
the people you hire to run these 
things as key to this, if that's true?

612
00:52:00,120 --> 00:52:04,760
In a lot of organizations, the people 
who buy SAFe, they have not run large  

613
00:52:04,760 --> 00:52:10,120
scale technology organizations before, or 
they're new to this way of working so they  

