00:52:10,120 --> 00:52:14,160
adopt SAFe and they hope it works because 
it looks like a nice plan, like we said,  

615
00:52:14,160 --> 00:52:19,360
to go out and do things. When you're doing 
a transformation, a lot of companies are  

616
00:52:19,360 --> 00:52:23,000
pulling people into these roles for the first 
time. I've said since day one that I've been  

